data.description: Start living in this inviting townhouse and be immediately welcomed by a grassy courtyard! Inside, the calming color scheme, high vaulted ceilings, & skylights create an open atmosphere, complemented by modern wood-look floors & a cozy fireplace. The galley kitchen boasts white cabinets, mosaic backsplash, butcher-block counters, a breakfast bar, & a lovely breakfast nook. Upstairs, you'll discover the primary bedroom & a loft area with sliding doors to a charming balcony. The downstairs bedroom & bathroom are great for guests! Serene backyard offers a covered patio, grass area, & two rear carport spaces totally fenced for added privacy. Don't let this gem slip by!
